data.description: Welcome to modern living in Independence Heights, one of Houston's fastest-growing neighborhoods! This sanctuary offers a dog park, guest parking, and proximity to Whole Foods, OrangeTheory, and Wakefield Crowbar. Enjoy quick access to major thoroughfares 610, 290, and 45. The second-floor main level features tall ceilings and abundant natural light, providing an open, airy and bright ambiance. The kitchen, an entertainer's dream, overlooks the family room, creating an ideal environment for entertainment. Flexibility reigns with secondary bedrooms on the first floor. Whether for guests, family, or a home office, the options are as versatile as your lifestyle. The primary bedroom on the second floor includes a spa-like bathroom with dual sinks, walk-in shower, and a tub. Don't miss this blend of luxury and convenience—schedule a showing today in the heart of Independence Heights! ASSUMABLE LOAN AVAILABLE!
